name: Baby Moana Lilo Dentist Games
description:
Ever wanted to be a dentist? Do you think you can do a better job than your local dentist?
Now is your chance. Become a dentist with this new Moana dentist game.
Take care of your famous patients. Whiten dirty teeth, clean their tongues and remove bad breath.
There are different patients to choose from. And each one has their own unique problems.

What are you waiting for? Download today!
